<BlogPost
  title="Why Claude Code ignores half your instructions (and how to fix it)"
  description="You tell Claude Code to use Tailwind. It reaches for styled-components. You say no semicolons. It adds them anyway. Here's why this happens and how to fix it with a better CLAUDE.md."
